 greetings, blessings, and grace onto Mohammad and the children and family of Mohammad, and Mohammad’s family to His own secrets, (Send your salutations, greetings, blessings, and grace onto Mohammad and the children and family of Mohammad) Place me in the army of your Imam the one who is the light for your believers, and assign me as one of his helpers.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "YAA MAN FAZZALA AALA IBRAAHEEMA WA AALA ISRAAEELA A’LAL A’ALA-MEENA BIKHTE-YAAREHI, WA AZHARA FEE MALAKOO-TIS SAMAA-WAATE WAL ARZE I’ZZA-TAQ TEDAA-REHI, WA AWDA-A’ MOHAMMADIN SALLAL LAAHO A’LAIY-HE WA AALE-HI WA AHLAL BAIYTE-HI GHARAA-E-BA AS-RAARE-HI, (SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE-HI), WAJ-A’LNEE MIN A’WAANE HUJJATE-KA A’LAA E’BAADE-KA WA ANSAARE-HI.", "ArabicText1": "یَا مَنْ فَضَّلَ آلَ اِبْرَاهِیْمَ وَآلَ اِسْرَائِیْلَ عَلَی الْعَالَمِیْنَ بِاخْتِیَارِهٖ، وَاَظْهَرَ فِیْ مَلَكُوْتِ السَّمَاوَاتِ وَالْاَرْضِ عِزِّۃَ اقْتِدَارِهٖ، وَاَوْدَعَ مُحَمَّدًا صَلَّی اللهُ عَلَیْهِ وَآلِهٖ وَاَهْلَ بَیْتِهٖ غَرَائِبَ اَسْرَارِهٖ، (صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِهٖ)، وَاجْعَلْنِیْ مِنْ اَعْوَانِ حُجَّتِكَ عَلٰی عِبَادِكَ وَاَنْصَارِهٖ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "Ara